** ER
E-01 REVERSING SELECT INSTRUCTION CAN NOT INPUT.
E-02 REVERSING SELECT INSTRUCTION IS 1
E-03 REVERSING UPDATE INSTRUCTION  CAN NOT INPUT.
E-04 REVERSING UPDATE INSTRUCTION IS  (0 1)
E-05 REVERSING DATA MAY NOT CANCEL.
E-06 REVERSING DATA NEED NOT REVIVE.
E-07 REVERSING NEW LOC OR EFFECTIVE DATE BIN ISN'T INPUT
E-08 REVERSING DATE OF EFFECTIVE DATE IS NOT RIGHT.
E-09 REVERSING EFFECTIVE DATE-BIN IS IT FROM SYSTEM DATE.
E-10 REVERSING DATAHAVE TO CANCEL BECAUSE KANBAN LIVES
E-11 REVERSING NEW LOCATION REPEAT.
E-12 CAN USE IT. INPUT IT IN INTRA-PROCESS LOCATION M/F
E-13 KANBAN KIND OF INTRA-PROCESS LOCATION M/F IS DIFFERENT.
E-14 REVERSING NEW LOCATION IS USED.
